1
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:13,000
"Double Helix"

2
00:01:56,600 --> 00:02:00,400
(Episode 10: We Got
Together When We Were 18)

3
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,800
Lu Feng.

4
00:02:27,639 --> 00:02:28,280
Lu Feng.

5
00:02:28,281 --> 00:02:30,281
Whatever it is, it can
wait until after my shower.

6
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,759
Isn't it time you let me go?

7
00:02:43,879 --> 00:02:46,279
What right do you have
to negotiate with me?

8
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:48,439
But what do you even want, keeping me here?

9
00:02:49,639 --> 00:02:51,319
You should have had your revenge by now.

10
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,720
There are plenty of people
willing to do what you want.

11
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,080
But what about me?

12
00:02:55,879 --> 00:02:57,240
I have nothing left now.

13
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,680
My brother.

14
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,240
My mother.

15
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,960
The people closest to me.

16
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:06,159
They're all gone now.

17
00:03:15,439 --> 00:03:17,120
How dare you bring up your mother?

18
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:19,520
How dare you bring up your brother?

19
00:03:21,639 --> 00:03:22,719
Don't you forget.

20
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,280
You abandoned me because of them.

21
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,879
You say you have no family.

22
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,919
What am I to you, then?

23
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,759
Let me tell you, Cheng Yichen.

24
00:03:45,039 --> 00:03:46,479
The way you've turned out...

25
00:03:47,759 --> 00:03:49,759
is the result of your own choices.

26
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,719
The mess I've become...

27
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:55,599
is all thanks to what you did...

28
00:03:55,759 --> 00:03:57,680
back then.

29
00:04:05,199 --> 00:04:07,879
It seems I've been too
good to you this time.

30
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:11,520
You still have the energy to make demands.

31
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,039
Is it because of Ke Lo?

32
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:16,200
Silent? I must have
hit the nail on the head.

33
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:17,879
Let me tell you something.

34
00:04:19,759 --> 00:04:21,360
He's younger than you.

35
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:23,160
Better looking.

36
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:25,959
He's better than you.

37
00:04:26,519 --> 00:04:28,160
A hundred times better.

38
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:35,040
You must be dreaming,
Cheng Yichen.

39
00:05:06,279 --> 00:05:07,839
Where do you think you can go?

40
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:12,480
I'm telling you.

41
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,959
I'll never let you leave me again.

42
00:05:18,639 --> 00:05:24,399
I'll make you stay by
my side forever and ever.

43
00:06:06,959 --> 00:06:07,959
You're awake.

44
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,400
Now that you're up, go downstairs.

45
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:26,759
You have an important
guest waiting for you.

46
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:42,839
Hurry up.

47
00:06:44,199 --> 00:06:45,279
Your guest...

48
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:47,000
is getting impatient.

49
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:17,680
Yichen, are you sick?

50
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:20,680
Why are your lips so pale?

51
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:23,959
And why are you covered in bruises?

52
00:07:25,233 --> 00:07:26,233
I'm not.

53
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,360
What are you doing here?

54
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,240
Did something happen?

55
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:32,399
I'm here to take you away.

56
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:34,399
Take him away?

57
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,879
You must be joking.

58
00:07:41,199 --> 00:07:42,399
Who are you to him?

59
00:07:42,839 --> 00:07:44,279
He's my husband.

60
00:07:45,519 --> 00:07:46,600
Husband?

61
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,480
Not anymore, I'd say.

62
00:07:55,199 --> 00:07:56,560
Even if you're not divorced,

63
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,519
has he fulfilled his duties as a husband?

64
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,079
Have you two ever even... done it?

65
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:06,560
Disgusting.

66
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:09,278
You have nothing to do with him now.

67
00:08:09,279 --> 00:08:11,319
What right do you have to
come here and demand him?

68
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:20,879
I simply invited him over...

69
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,360
as a guest.

70
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:25,920
To catch up on old times.

71
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,680
To have a chat.

72
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,400
Is there a problem with that?

73
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,720
A guest?

74
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:37,798
You took his phone.

75
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,959
You locked him in your house.

76
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,600
What kind of guest is that?

77
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,039
Besides,

78
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:44,440
you and Yichen are not related in any way.

79
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:47,320
What right do you have
to invite him as a guest?

80
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:51,720
Yichen, you want to leave, right?

81
00:08:58,799 --> 00:08:59,919
Not related?

82
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,120
Do you have any idea...

83
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:07,919
what your husband and I...

84
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,080
Get out.

85
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,360
Cheng Yichen.

86
00:09:15,399 --> 00:09:16,960
Tell this so-called wife of yours...

87
00:09:20,159 --> 00:09:21,399
who I am to you.

88
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:46,200
Don't touch him.

89
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,440
What we've done together...

90
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,799
you have no idea.

91
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,320
Zhuo Lan, let me tell you.

92
00:10:28,279 --> 00:10:29,519
Your husband and I...

93
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,960
got together when we were 18.

94
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,799
We were sleeping together at 18.

95
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,559
Stop talking.

96
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,039
You say he's your husband.

97
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,320
But what about you?

98
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,720
What have you two done?

99
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:03,240
What have you done?

100
00:11:03,279 --> 00:11:03,840
Tell me.

101
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,360
Say it!

102
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:04,960
Shut up!

103
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,879
Go to hell!

104
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,440
No!

105
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:23,919
Lu Feng.

106
00:11:24,759 --> 00:11:26,519
I should hate you.

107
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:29,679
So why am I lying here in front of you?

108
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,200
Maybe this is for the best.

109
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:35,159
In the end, going back in time...

110
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:37,639
it's as if nothing ever happened.

111
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:41,399
Cheng Yichen, what a coincidence.

112
00:11:42,159 --> 00:11:43,159
Lu Feng.

113
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,679
I need you to promise me one thing.

114
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:51,320
As long as I don't have a girlfriend,

115
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:54,320
can you promise not
to fall for any other girls?

116
00:11:57,879 --> 00:11:59,200
I just like you.

117
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,399
What's wrong with that?

118
00:12:04,279 --> 00:12:05,440
I guess...

119
00:12:06,279 --> 00:12:08,000
there's nothing wrong with it.

120
00:12:21,759 --> 00:12:23,039
I want to be with you.

121
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:24,720
Forever.

122
00:12:25,159 --> 00:12:26,440
Forever.

123
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,440
Lu Feng.

124
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:37,440
I love you.

125
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,039
I love you, too.

126
00:12:58,639 --> 00:12:59,639
Long time no see.

127
00:13:01,559 --> 00:13:02,679
After the New Year,

128
00:13:03,279 --> 00:13:05,039
if I still insist on being with you,

129
00:13:05,919 --> 00:13:07,599
I'll no longer be a part of the Lu family.

130
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:09,039
We...

131
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,879
will always be together.

132
00:13:12,919 --> 00:13:13,919
I,

133
00:13:14,519 --> 00:13:15,519
Lu Feng,

134
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,360
for the rest of my life,

135
00:13:18,559 --> 00:13:19,799
will never leave Cheng Yichen.

136
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:21,159
It's another year, Lu Feng.

137
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,600
Another year.

138
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,520
You have to stay with me this year.

139
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:27,799
And next year.

140
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,200
And the year after that.

141
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,000
And the year after that.

142
00:13:43,759 --> 00:13:44,840
Don't fall asleep.

143
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:53,360
Don't fall asleep.

144
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:54,639
Don't fall asleep.

145
00:13:54,759 --> 00:13:55,759
Don't fall asleep.

146
00:13:56,919 --> 00:13:57,919
Xiao Chen.

147
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,720
Xiao Chen.

148
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:04,840
Bro.

149
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,000
Yi-chen.

150
00:14:12,799 --> 00:14:13,799
What's wrong?

151
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:15,000
Are you not feeling well?

152
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:16,120
I'm fine.

153
00:14:16,879 --> 00:14:17,919
I just need a moment.

154
00:14:21,399 --> 00:14:22,399
Drink some water.

155
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,440
What's wrong?

156
00:14:32,279 --> 00:14:33,480
I don't know.

157
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:35,720
Qin Lang.

158
00:14:36,279 --> 00:14:37,960
This feeling is so familiar.

159
00:14:40,399 --> 00:14:42,399
Do you think something
happened to my brother?

160
00:14:43,279 --> 00:14:44,279
Of course not.

161
00:14:44,679 --> 00:14:45,679
Don't overthink it.

162
00:14:46,679 --> 00:14:48,119
But you've been looking for so long.

163
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,799
Is there really no news at all?

164
00:14:51,639 --> 00:14:53,519
All I know is that your
brother is in Xincheng.

165
00:14:53,799 --> 00:14:55,240
I can't find anything else.

166
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:58,200
It's like someone is deliberately
blocking the information.

167
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,320
Then let's go to Xincheng.

168
00:15:01,159 --> 00:15:02,679
I can't wait another day.

169
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,120
Whatever you say.

170
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:12,399
Yichen, quick, hurry!

171
00:15:12,639 --> 00:15:13,639
Yichen!

172
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:15,799
Yichen, wake up! Yichen!

173
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:17,960
Yichen!

174
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:18,799
Xiao Chen! Yichen!

175
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:20,000
Doctor, you have to save him!

176
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:20,440
Xiao Chen!

177
00:15:20,441 --> 00:15:21,721
Family members, please stay out.

178
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:37,240
You bastard.

179
00:15:37,799 --> 00:15:39,679
What the hell do you want?

180
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:42,200
Are you satisfied now?

181
00:15:43,639 --> 00:15:45,399
What if Yichen dies?

182
00:15:50,559 --> 00:15:52,959
Five years ago, I was the one
who forced him to get married.

183
00:15:53,879 --> 00:15:56,039
In these five years, nothing
ever happened between us.

184
00:15:56,559 --> 00:15:57,960
From the very beginning,

185
00:15:58,440 --> 00:15:59,639
you were the one he loved.

186
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:01,720
And you?

187
00:16:03,519 --> 00:16:06,360
You're just a bastard who
only ever thinks about himself.

188
00:16:08,159 --> 00:16:09,240
Yichen.

189
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:12,039
Yichen.

190
00:16:15,279 --> 00:16:16,679
I went to find you...

191
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,360
because I wanted to apologize.

192
00:16:19,480 --> 00:16:20,919
For five years ago.

193
00:16:22,279 --> 00:16:23,320
I'm sorry.

194
00:16:24,039 --> 00:16:26,960
My mind was such a mess back then.

195
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:28,360
My brother...

196
00:16:28,519 --> 00:16:31,000
and my mom, with what
suddenly happened to them...

197
00:16:32,399 --> 00:16:35,240
I just didn't know what to do.

198
00:16:35,879 --> 00:16:38,559
Lu Feng, let's talk.

199
00:16:38,919 --> 00:16:39,919
Talk about what?

200
00:16:40,559 --> 00:16:41,799
About how you betrayed me?

201
00:16:43,039 --> 00:16:44,959
Back then, it was because
of my mom and my brother.

202
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:45,960
I had no choice.

203
00:16:46,879 --> 00:16:49,159
Plenty of people would
love to do what you want.

204
00:16:49,519 --> 00:16:50,519
But what about me?

205
00:16:51,279 --> 00:16:52,440
I have nothing now.

206
00:16:53,919 --> 00:16:54,960
My brother.

207
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:56,600
My mom.

208
00:16:57,279 --> 00:16:58,279
The people closest to me.

209
00:16:59,480 --> 00:17:01,559
Now they're all gone.

210
00:17:50,704 --> 00:17:53,888
(Three months later)

211
00:18:02,119 --> 00:18:03,119
Hold on.

212
00:18:10,599 --> 00:18:11,920
Mr. Lu, you're here.

213
00:18:12,319 --> 00:18:13,358
You're so punctual every day.

214
00:18:13,359 --> 00:18:14,480
That's really something.

215
00:18:39,519 --> 00:18:40,519
Xiao Chen.

216
00:18:41,519 --> 00:18:43,279
The temperature suddenly dropped today.

217
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:46,200
I bought you a new jacket.

218
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:49,799
I think this style suits you.

219
00:18:50,559 --> 00:18:53,480
I just don't know if you'll like the color.

220
00:18:54,119 --> 00:18:56,680
I also went out of my way to
buy your favorite soup dumplings.

221
00:18:57,319 --> 00:18:58,319
And orange juice.

222
00:19:10,839 --> 00:19:11,839
Here.

223
00:19:21,359 --> 00:19:22,480
If you want to eat,

224
00:19:24,079 --> 00:19:25,160
then hurry up and wake up.

225
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:44,280
Where did we leave off yesterday?

226
00:19:45,319 --> 00:19:46,319
Ke Lo.

227
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:50,599
Ke Lo is actually my sister's son.

228
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:53,200
He's a sophomore in college this year.

229
00:19:53,599 --> 00:19:55,519
He came to intern at my
company over the summer.

230
00:19:57,880 --> 00:20:00,000
He didn't want anyone to
know about our relationship.

231
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:03,880
One day, he came up and asked me...

232
00:20:04,799 --> 00:20:06,640
if the company was hiring.

233
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:10,160
He said he'd found a
talented person for me.

234
00:20:12,519 --> 00:20:13,839
I never thought...

235
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:17,039
I'd hear your name from him.

236
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:23,200
I only found out today
that you live in Xincheng.

237
00:20:24,799 --> 00:20:26,359
It turns out it's so close to Lancheng.

238
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:34,400
The Zhuo family really
hid you well all these years.

239
00:20:37,240 --> 00:20:39,119
I had to use work as an excuse...

240
00:20:39,799 --> 00:20:41,359
just to find out any news about you.

241
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:55,200
I went looking for you before.

242
00:20:57,680 --> 00:20:59,920
But I saw you and Zhuo Lan,
looking like a happy couple.

243
00:21:01,839 --> 00:21:02,880
You looked so happy.

244
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:08,279
I really hated you back then.

245
00:21:09,480 --> 00:21:11,480
I couldn't understand how
you could just leave me.

246
00:21:13,519 --> 00:21:15,200
And let me suffer alone for so long.

247
00:21:19,960 --> 00:21:22,599
While you got to live so well.

248
00:21:29,519 --> 00:21:31,319
I really wanted to destroy you.

249
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,559
To make you...

250
00:21:35,200 --> 00:21:36,599
suffer just like me.

251
00:21:39,960 --> 00:21:42,400
But the first time you appeared before me,

252
00:21:43,960 --> 00:21:45,400
the only thing I could think was,

253
00:21:48,599 --> 00:21:49,799
'Are you doing okay?'

254
00:22:19,359 --> 00:22:20,359
Xiao Chen.

255
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:26,759
When on earth are you going to wake up?

256
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:02,480
Let's go.

257
00:23:34,440 --> 00:23:35,440
Xiao Chen.

258
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:37,480
I have some good news to share with you.

259
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:40,799
I finally succeeded in acquiring
our company's biggest competitor.

260
00:23:41,160 --> 00:23:42,640
Now, our company's market value...

261
00:23:43,279 --> 00:23:44,879
is number one in the entire province.

262
00:23:51,359 --> 00:23:52,400
In my entire life,

263
00:23:53,319 --> 00:23:54,559
whatever I've wanted to do,

264
00:23:55,079 --> 00:23:56,199
whatever I've wanted to get,

265
00:23:57,759 --> 00:23:58,759
I've always been able to.

266
00:24:02,359 --> 00:24:03,359
Except for you.

267
00:24:04,799 --> 00:24:06,000
No matter what I do,

268
00:24:06,519 --> 00:24:07,599
how much I give,

269
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:09,240
I still can't have you.

270
00:24:23,599 --> 00:24:24,799
Now...

271
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:27,480
isn't this pretty good too?

272
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:29,839
Lying here quietly.

273
00:24:30,519 --> 00:24:32,039
You won't suddenly disappear.

274
00:24:34,559 --> 00:24:35,920
And you won't suddenly leave me.

275
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:40,240
It's as if...

276
00:24:40,519 --> 00:24:42,519
you truly and completely belong to me.

277
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:53,200
But, Xiao Chen,

278
00:24:54,039 --> 00:24:55,920
if you never wake up,

279
00:24:58,599 --> 00:25:00,440
then what's the point of me being alive?

280
00:25:26,519 --> 00:25:27,519
I'm sorry.

281
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:32,039
I'm so sorry, Yichen.

282
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:20,160
Xiao Chen.

283
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:23,480
The doctor said...

284
00:26:24,960 --> 00:26:26,599
you can actually hear everything.

285
00:26:30,119 --> 00:26:31,759
It's you who doesn't want to wake up yet.

286
00:26:33,279 --> 00:26:34,839
You must still be angry with me, right?

287
00:26:42,200 --> 00:26:44,360
When I thought about you
being someone else's husband,

288
00:26:46,279 --> 00:26:48,039
I lost all reason.

289
00:26:51,680 --> 00:26:53,880
I arranged for those people
to put on an act with me.

290
00:26:55,079 --> 00:26:56,480
It was all to make you angry.

291
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:03,839
I'm not actually into men at all.

292
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:10,440
I only like you.

293
00:27:11,680 --> 00:27:12,680
From the very beginning,

294
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,240
I've only ever liked you.

295
00:27:19,839 --> 00:27:21,480
What I want is...

296
00:27:22,720 --> 00:27:24,000
only you.

297
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:32,480
Why do you always want to leave me?

298
00:27:34,160 --> 00:27:35,160
Xiao Chen.

299
00:27:35,720 --> 00:27:37,359
Please, wake up soon.

300
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:41,119
Even if you wake up
and tell me you hate me,

301
00:27:42,119 --> 00:27:43,119
that would be fine.

302
00:27:44,119 --> 00:27:46,319
I just want to hear your voice.

303
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:51,200
I haven't heard your voice in so long.

304
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:55,079
I just want to see you smile.

305
00:28:13,279 --> 00:28:15,200
Where on earth do you think my brother is?

306
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:16,799
He must be in Xincheng.

307
00:28:17,119 --> 00:28:18,960
But we've been looking for so long.

308
00:28:19,559 --> 00:28:21,400
How can there be no news at all?

309
00:28:23,039 --> 00:28:24,039
Qin Lang.

310
00:28:24,519 --> 00:28:25,599
This makes no sense.

311
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:30,000
Do you think my brother
is hiding on his own,

312
00:28:30,839 --> 00:28:32,599
or did someone hide him?

313
00:28:34,599 --> 00:28:35,599
It's hard to say.

314
00:28:35,759 --> 00:28:36,160
How about this?

315
00:28:36,759 --> 00:28:38,279
I'll contact Shen Chao later.

316
00:28:38,440 --> 00:28:39,759
See if he has any connections.

317
00:28:41,799 --> 00:28:42,799
Are you hungry?

318
00:28:43,079 --> 00:28:44,239
Want to get something to eat?

319
00:28:44,440 --> 00:28:45,440
I don't have an appetite.

320
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:46,720
I don't want to eat.

321
00:28:47,440 --> 00:28:49,480
You have to eat even if
you don't have an appetite.

322
00:28:49,599 --> 00:28:51,039
I saw a restaurant nearby.

323
00:28:51,240 --> 00:28:52,320
It has pretty good reviews.

324
00:28:52,880 --> 00:28:53,920
Don't you love spicy food?

325
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:55,880
Get changed.

326
00:28:56,319 --> 00:28:57,319
I'll take you.

327
00:28:59,359 --> 00:29:00,920
My brother likes spicy food too.

328
00:29:02,079 --> 00:29:03,079
What?

329
00:29:07,039 --> 00:29:08,920
I said my brother likes spicy food too.

330
00:29:09,319 --> 00:29:10,880
His taste is the same as mine.

331
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,680
We'll find him.

332
00:29:59,119 --> 00:30:00,599
Don't you love apples the most?

333
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:02,400
I've been practicing every day.

334
00:30:03,079 --> 00:30:04,079
Now,

335
00:30:06,319 --> 00:30:07,880
I can peel them really beautifully.

336
00:30:10,359 --> 00:30:12,240
This is your favorite rabbit shape.

337
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:21,440
I peeled this apple for you.

338
00:30:25,400 --> 00:30:27,039
Can you please wake up?

339
00:30:58,319 --> 00:30:59,319
Xiao Chen.

340
00:31:00,039 --> 00:31:01,400
If you wake up,

341
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:03,880
we'll never be apart again.

342
00:31:05,359 --> 00:31:07,559
Whatever kind of Valentine's
Day you want to celebrate,

343
00:31:08,079 --> 00:31:09,759
White Day, Green Day,

344
00:31:10,079 --> 00:31:11,480
I'll celebrate them all with you.

345
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:20,599
The lifetime I promised you,

346
00:31:24,200 --> 00:31:26,119
I'm still waiting for you.

347
00:31:47,680 --> 00:31:48,759
Lu...

348
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:51,400
Feng.

349
00:31:57,200 --> 00:31:58,200
Lu...

350
00:31:59,720 --> 00:32:00,720
Feng.

351
00:33:11,799 --> 00:33:12,799
Boss, I'm heading out.

352
00:33:12,960 --> 00:33:13,559
See you tomorrow.

353
00:33:13,960 --> 00:33:14,400
Be safe.

354
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:15,400
Okay.

355
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:26,200
Sorry, we're closed.

356
00:33:33,039 --> 00:33:34,039
Yichen.

357
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:36,240
I'm really sorry.

358
00:33:36,319 --> 00:33:37,319
You're at it again.

359
00:33:37,839 --> 00:33:38,880
I already told you.

360
00:33:39,240 --> 00:33:41,000
We don't say things
like that to each other.

361
00:33:41,599 --> 00:33:43,159
Besides, if we're really keeping score,

362
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:44,680
I'm the one who should be sorry.

363
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:45,880
I wasted you...

364
00:33:46,640 --> 00:33:48,880
and held you back during
the best years of your life.

365
00:33:49,720 --> 00:33:51,359
You didn't hold me back at all.

366
00:33:51,599 --> 00:33:53,119
In fact, you helped me a lot.

367
00:33:53,359 --> 00:33:55,240
If it weren't for all these years together,

368
00:33:55,319 --> 00:33:57,719
I'm afraid I never would have
been able to move on from you.

369
00:34:00,039 --> 00:34:01,839
I've completely made peace with it.

370
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,000
You need to as well.

371
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:06,079
Just running away...

372
00:34:06,559 --> 00:34:07,880
won't solve any problems.

373
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:52,920
We took in a lot of cash this month.

374
00:34:53,159 --> 00:34:54,280
So I won't deposit it.

375
00:34:54,559 --> 00:34:55,856
This is the part to pay you back.

376
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:56,880
You should count it.

377
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:11,360
Xiao Chen.

378
00:35:12,079 --> 00:35:13,079
Can you please...

379
00:35:13,639 --> 00:35:15,360
not be so formal with me about money?

380
00:35:16,199 --> 00:35:17,719
You've already helped me so much.

381
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:20,760
You don't have to pay for my
hospital bills on top of everything else.

382
00:35:26,519 --> 00:35:28,239
Can I use your restroom?

383
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:32,320
Sure.

384
00:35:53,519 --> 00:35:55,519
Do you have any news
about Yi-chen and the others?

385
00:35:56,760 --> 00:35:58,480
I only know they're abroad.

386
00:35:59,280 --> 00:36:01,400
I haven't found out
which country specifically.

387
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:03,360
It's all my fault.

388
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:05,480
I deleted all their contact
information back then.

389
00:36:05,639 --> 00:36:06,919
And deactivated all my accounts.

390
00:36:08,159 --> 00:36:09,159
Don't worry.

391
00:36:09,760 --> 00:36:11,360
I'll keep looking.

392
00:36:12,199 --> 00:36:13,239
I'm sure I can find them.

393
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:14,840
Sorry to trouble you.

394
00:36:26,079 --> 00:36:27,239
The restroom is over there.

395
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:31,040
The lightbulb seems to be out.

396
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:37,280
Let me get it.

397
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,119
You just recovered.

398
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:46,080
You shouldn't be
climbing all over the place.

399
00:37:28,360 --> 00:37:29,360
There.

400
00:37:43,800 --> 00:37:44,800
I just saw...

401
00:37:45,400 --> 00:37:46,840
there's instant ramen over there.

402
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:49,719
Can you make me a bowl of instant noodles?

403
00:38:12,880 --> 00:38:13,880
Thank you.

404
00:39:23,599 --> 00:39:24,599
Xiao Chen.

405
00:39:32,559 --> 00:39:33,559
It's okay.

406
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:54,920
Xiao Chen.

407
00:39:56,159 --> 00:39:57,320
Today is Valentine's Day.

408
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:11,680
I'll always be waiting for you.

409
00:40:29,199 --> 00:40:30,199
Happy Valentine's Day.

410
00:41:12,599 --> 00:41:13,119
Boss.

411
00:41:13,360 --> 00:41:14,639
Order whatever you want.

412
00:41:14,920 --> 00:41:16,535
They have your favorite,
the hot and sour kind.

413
00:41:16,559 --> 00:41:17,559
Don't be shy.

414
00:41:18,480 --> 00:41:19,720
How's the interview prep going?

415
00:41:20,159 --> 00:41:21,159
I'm feeling confident.

416
00:41:21,199 --> 00:41:22,320
You've got this.

417
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:24,719
Boss, you're too kind.

418
00:41:25,039 --> 00:41:26,039
I quit so suddenly,

419
00:41:26,199 --> 00:41:27,320
but you didn't dock my pay.

420
00:41:27,400 --> 00:41:29,119
You even paid me my salary in advance.

421
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:31,360
I'm sure you'll have nothing
but good fortune ahead.

422
00:41:31,519 --> 00:41:33,558
You've helped me out so
much these past few months.

423
00:41:33,559 --> 00:41:34,678
I'm already very grateful.

424
00:41:34,679 --> 00:41:36,359
There's no reason for me to dock your pay.

425
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:37,199
Thanks, Boss.

426
00:41:37,199 --> 00:41:38,199
What do you want to eat?

427
00:41:38,239 --> 00:41:38,960
Hot and sour pork intestines.

428
00:41:38,960 --> 00:41:39,960
Sure.

429
00:41:41,159 --> 00:41:42,598
Let's see what else they have.

430
00:41:42,599 --> 00:41:43,719
Yichen, are you okay?

431
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:45,400
I'm sorry, sir.

432
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:46,400
I'm so sorry.

433
00:41:46,559 --> 00:41:47,759
Watch where you're going!

434
00:41:47,760 --> 00:41:49,000
It's fine. It wasn't hot water.

435
00:41:49,159 --> 00:41:50,159
It's okay.

436
00:42:10,920 --> 00:42:11,920
Yichen.

437
00:42:13,159 --> 00:42:14,159
Bro.

438
00:42:16,960 --> 00:42:17,960
Bro.

439
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:32,000
Bro.

440
00:43:03,280 --> 00:43:05,039
Bro, look. My leg is really all better.

441
00:43:10,320 --> 00:43:11,320
Alright, you two.

442
00:43:11,639 --> 00:43:12,880
If you two keep crying,

443
00:43:13,079 --> 00:43:14,599
you're going to flood the whole hotel.

444
00:43:15,159 --> 00:43:16,840
Go get your own room.

445
00:43:17,119 --> 00:43:18,119
Don't bother us.

446
00:43:18,519 --> 00:43:20,440
I haven't seen Xiao Chen in years either.

447
00:43:20,679 --> 00:43:22,079
Can't we all catch up?

448
00:43:27,920 --> 00:43:29,159
Let's go, Bro. Upstairs.

449
00:43:53,360 --> 00:43:54,360
Xiao Chen.

450
00:43:54,960 --> 00:43:55,960
Xiao Chen.

451
00:43:56,519 --> 00:43:57,519
Xiao Chen.

452
00:43:58,159 --> 00:43:59,159
Bro.

453
00:43:59,400 --> 00:44:00,840
Why are you so thin?

454
00:44:03,239 --> 00:44:04,679
I was sick for a while.

455
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:06,679
But I'm all better now.

456
00:44:07,239 --> 00:44:08,239
By the way,

457
00:44:08,440 --> 00:44:09,560
what brings you to Xincheng?

458
00:44:10,559 --> 00:44:11,599
I came looking for you.

459
00:44:12,280 --> 00:44:14,120
Why did you cut off
contact with me back then?

460
00:44:15,199 --> 00:44:16,199
After Mom passed away,

461
00:44:18,119 --> 00:44:19,575
you didn't want your
little brother anymore?

462
00:44:19,599 --> 00:44:20,639
Of course not.

463
00:44:21,519 --> 00:44:22,800
At the time,

464
00:44:24,440 --> 00:44:25,760
my head was just a mess.

465
00:44:27,039 --> 00:44:28,079
And I got married.

466
00:44:29,000 --> 00:44:30,760
I was afraid Lu Feng
would come back for me.

467
00:44:30,800 --> 00:44:33,480
I was even more afraid he would hurt you guys.

468
00:44:34,239 --> 00:44:34,679
So...

469
00:44:34,679 --> 00:44:35,039
Wait.

470
00:44:35,679 --> 00:44:36,920
You really got married?

471
00:44:38,400 --> 00:44:39,400
You know...

472
00:44:40,039 --> 00:44:41,639
Mom's situation at the time...

473
00:44:42,519 --> 00:44:43,519
I had no choice.

474
00:44:43,719 --> 00:44:46,199
But marriage isn't something
you can just jump into.

475
00:44:46,840 --> 00:44:47,960
Who did you marry?

476
00:44:48,239 --> 00:44:49,239
It's not important.

477
00:44:49,800 --> 00:44:51,039
It was in name only.

478
00:44:51,400 --> 00:44:52,599
And we're already divorced.

479
00:44:53,480 --> 00:44:55,840
She's found her own happiness now, too.

480
00:44:59,880 --> 00:45:00,880
Bro.

481
00:45:01,800 --> 00:45:04,320
What happened with you and Lu Feng?

482
00:45:05,400 --> 00:45:06,400
Did you know?

483
00:45:06,519 --> 00:45:07,519
He's in Xincheng, too.

484
00:45:07,599 --> 00:45:08,639
How did you know?

485
00:45:08,800 --> 00:45:10,000
He's so famous.

486
00:45:10,800 --> 00:45:13,480
A self-made tech mogul.

487
00:45:13,679 --> 00:45:15,719
He's made headlines many times.

488
00:45:16,320 --> 00:45:17,760
Qin Lang did wonder...

489
00:45:18,039 --> 00:45:20,119
if you might be with him.

490
00:45:20,559 --> 00:45:21,880
But I didn't think so.

491
00:45:22,679 --> 00:45:24,280
After everything that happened.

492
00:45:25,519 --> 00:45:26,519
Bro.

493
00:45:27,039 --> 00:45:28,559
After you came to Xincheng,

494
00:45:28,920 --> 00:45:30,239
you haven't seen him again,

495
00:45:31,360 --> 00:45:32,360
right?

496
00:45:42,239 --> 00:45:43,800
Actually, I've thought about it since.

497
00:45:44,960 --> 00:45:46,320
The thing with me and Qin Lang...

498
00:45:46,840 --> 00:45:48,480
Mom would have found out sooner or later.

499
00:45:48,760 --> 00:45:51,440
Lu Feng just brought
it to light a little earlier.

500
00:45:52,199 --> 00:45:53,400
I can't blame it all on him.

501
00:45:54,679 --> 00:45:56,440
He didn't push me on purpose.

502
00:45:57,800 --> 00:45:59,119
I provoked him, too.

503
00:46:00,159 --> 00:46:01,159
Bro.

504
00:46:01,800 --> 00:46:04,639
You can't always try
to be good to everyone.

505
00:46:05,679 --> 00:46:07,159
Trying not to hurt anyone's feelings.

506
00:46:07,280 --> 00:46:08,599
No one can be that noble.

507
00:46:10,639 --> 00:46:11,639
Be a little selfish.

508
00:46:13,079 --> 00:46:14,599
You'll be happier.

509
00:46:21,960 --> 00:46:22,960
Bro.

510
00:46:23,920 --> 00:46:25,000
Come abroad with me.

511
00:46:25,280 --> 00:46:26,759
Since you're on your own now,

512
00:46:26,760 --> 00:46:28,679
it would be better for you to be with me.

513
00:46:29,079 --> 00:46:30,079
From now on,

514
00:46:30,920 --> 00:46:32,039
I'll take care of you.

515
00:46:35,159 --> 00:46:36,159
Okay?

516
00:47:24,719 --> 00:47:25,719
Let me tell you,

517
00:47:26,320 --> 00:47:29,119
I spent a long time looking for this house.

518
00:47:30,239 --> 00:47:31,839
I thought the environment here was nice,

519
00:47:32,039 --> 00:47:33,960
and you can see the blue sky so clearly.

520
00:47:40,360 --> 00:47:42,519
Shen Chao has connections in Xincheng.

521
00:47:43,000 --> 00:47:44,480
I can entrust the coffee shop to him.

522
00:47:44,719 --> 00:47:46,239
If he can run it, great.

523
00:47:46,519 --> 00:47:48,119
If not, he can sell it.

524
00:47:55,800 --> 00:47:56,800
Xiao Chen.

525
00:47:59,719 --> 00:48:01,039
How did you find this place?

526
00:48:01,719 --> 00:48:03,800
I knew there was a reason
we couldn't find Yichen.

527
00:48:04,519 --> 00:48:05,799
You were behind it, weren't you?

528
00:48:07,760 --> 00:48:09,199
Are you here to take him away?

529
00:48:11,480 --> 00:48:13,440
Do you have any news
about Yichen and the others?

530
00:48:15,480 --> 00:48:17,000
I only know they're abroad.

531
00:48:17,559 --> 00:48:20,320
I don't know which
country specifically yet.

532
00:48:22,199 --> 00:48:23,760
You knew where they were all along.

533
00:48:25,800 --> 00:48:26,880
You found them,

534
00:48:27,679 --> 00:48:29,039
just so you could leave with them.

535
00:48:29,400 --> 00:48:30,400
Isn't that right?

536
00:48:34,119 --> 00:48:35,320
Can't I leave?

